    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. Mechanically, it is very reliable, with a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that performs well in both city and highway driving. While the exterior and interior show some light signs of regular use, such as minor surface scratches and slight upholstery wear, the car is structurally sound and aesthetically pleasing. It is a dependable choice for anyone seeking a quality pre-owned vehicle that is ready for the road.",
