    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies both performance and reliability. This unit has undergone a comprehensive inspection to ensure it meets our exacting standards for mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. Featuring a documented service history and a well-preserved interior, it offers a refined driving experience for the discerning buyer. We invite you to experience the superior handling and sophisticated comfort of this distinguished automobile.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and she's been such a joy to drive! It's in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years. It's the perfect reliable daily driver that still looks great pulling into any driveway. I've kept up with the maintenance, so it's all ready for its next adventure with you! Feel free to reach out with any questions at all\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great new home!",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 1995 BMW M3 featuring the S50B30 inline-six engine, renowned for its linear power delivery and robust iron-block construction. This example retains its factory ZF 5-speed manual gearbox and a 3.15 limited-slip differential, ensuring a visceral, analog driving experience. The cooling system has been proactively addressed with an aluminum radiator and high-flow water pump, mitigating the common failure points of this platform. The suspension utilizes a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup, providing the neutral handling balance and 50/50 weight distribution the E36 chassis is celebrated for. Recent maintenance includes a VANOS unit refresh and new trailing arm bushings. While the exterior shows honest character from spirited use, the mechanical vitals remain strong, offering a turnkey entry into M-division ownership.",
      "price": 31800.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used sedan. Good condition. Well-maintained engine. Clean interior. Minimal exterior wear. Ready for immediate use.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and practicality, maintained with a high level of care. The exterior paint still holds a brilliant shine, though upon close inspection, you will find a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and one small, shallow scratch near the trunk\u2014honest wear that reflects regular use. The alloy wheels are in great shape with no significant curb rash. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free. The leather upholstery is soft and well-preserved, showing only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, while the carpets and headliner remain spotless. All electronics, from the touchscreen navigation to the heated seats and sunroof, are fully operational. Under the hood, the car is mechanically robust. It has been serviced religiously at scheduled intervals; most recently, I had the fluids flushed and a fresh set of tires installed. It starts promptly, idles smoothly, and provides a confident, quiet ride. This is a dependable, high-quality car that is ready for the road immediately.",
      "price": 33800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, which exemplifies a harmonious balance of performance and sophisticated design. This unit has undergone a rigorous inspection to ensure its mechanical integrity and aesthetic standards meet our exacting requirements. Offering a refined driving experience and a well-appointed interior, this vehicle represents a premier selection for the discerning professional seeking both value and distinction. We invite you to witness firsthand the superior craftsmanship and reliable history that define this exceptional offering.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still looks fantastic on the road? This beauty has been well-loved and runs like an absolute dream. It\u2019s got a bit of character but is super dependable for your daily commute or those fun weekend getaways. It's clean, comfy, and ready for its next adventure with you! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis retains its signature 50/50 weight distribution, with the suspension geometry providing exceptional turn-in and feedback. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including VANOS system servicing and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring the structural integrity matches its performance capabilities. A mechanically robust driver\u2019s car ready for the canyon or the track.",
